name: Admiring Gustav
description:
Those black & white rectangles on the man's robe that makes it firm and strong is balanced out by those floating flowers on the woman's dress. For me, those black & white rectangles & flowers was more important than the sea of gold around them two people kissing (About The Kiss by Gustav Klimt)

Admiring Gustav was my attempt to emulate that  kind of composition, detail, form, and material. But instead of gold, I use trash.

Admiring Gustav - Analog Collage made from paper trash in November 2017
